

Do you want to be part of the ongoing digitalization of the maritime industry and contribute to Ulstein Group's digital future? 

You will be joining Ulstein's team of data engineers and data scientists to develop, support, and facilitate the ongoing development of digital services for vessels in operations and the digitalization of shipbuilding and ship design services at Ulstein. We believe digitalization will play a significant role in making shipping operations and shipbuilding smarter, and in the ongoing decarbonization of shipping operations. You, as a Data Engineer, will make a significant contribution to this initiative. 

Ulstein  seeks a Data Engineer with some experience in big-data analytics, data collection, collation, storage, and retrieval. The core function as Data Engineer will be to design, build, and maintain systems and infrastructure for collection, storage, and processing of raw data on Ulstein's data platform. 

 

